  "interpretation": "All three pattern types materialize on SW 2024 SP1 (rev 32.1.0). KEY FINDING: FeatureLinearPattern5 silently rejects ICE (Instant3D) seed features (type 'ICE' from CreateCircleByRadius-based extrusions) but works with standard Extrusion seeds. Circular pattern (FeatureCircularPattern5) and mirror (InsertMirrorFeature2) work with any seed type. All three return the feature object (RETURN_VALUE contract, like sweep; no count-delta needed). Seed selection works via _find_feature_by_name + IFeature.Select2(append, mark) — the feature_add path has no direct IFeature reference but can look up by tree-name. Direction/axis/plane selection uses the proven SelectByID (5-arg) + SetSelectedObjectMark pattern from the build-spec builder."
